  "text": "Training the three models, and calculating the marginals, now has a grammar constant equal to the number of non-terminals in the grammar, which is far more manageable. We use the algorithm described in [CITATION_1] to train the conditional log-linear model; this method was found to converge to a good model after 10 iterations over the training data.",
